HEADWORD: Multiserial
<hw>Mul`ti*se"ri*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Multi-</ets> + <ets>serial</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Arranged in many rows, or series, as the scales of a pine cone, or
the leaves of the houseleek.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Multisiliquous</ent>⟦br⟧
